      <title>斯里兰卡总统计划启动国际货币基金组织会谈，重点关注稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/sri-lanka-president-plans-to-start-imf-talks-focus-on-stability</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯里兰卡新任总统阿努拉·库马拉·迪萨纳亚克表示，他计划在推出其他举措之前，先与国际货币基金组织展开讨论，作为建立岛国稳定工作的重点之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/sri-lanka-president-plans-to-start-imf-talks-focus-on-stability</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 15:21:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国改变对海地政策，在资金短缺的情况下派遣联合国特派团</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/us-changes-tack-on-haiti-pitching-un-mission-amid-scant-funding</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国希望将去年为解决海地安全危机而提出的资金短缺的警察任务转变为联合国维和行动，希望正式安排能让更多资金流入这个加勒比国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/us-changes-tack-on-haiti-pitching-un-mission-amid-scant-funding</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 15:10:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>为什么真主党比哈马斯更让以色列担心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/hezbollah-why-the-lebanese-militia-is-more-worrying-to-israel-than-hamas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自哈马斯 10 月 7 日与以色列发动新一轮战争以来，黎巴嫩民兵组织真主党通过军事行动表达了对巴勒斯坦伊斯兰组织的声援。真主党几乎每天都向以色列北部发射导弹、迫击炮、火箭弹和爆炸性无人机，迫使以色列也以火力予以回击。9 月底，战斗进一步升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/hezbollah-why-the-lebanese-militia-is-more-worrying-to-israel-than-hamas</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 14:31:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合国估计洪水导致 850 万尼日利亚人失去粮食</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/floods-destroy-food-for-8-5-million-nigerians-un-estimates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国粮食及农业组织估计，在收获季节开始时洪水淹没了尼日利亚部分地区，毁坏了可供 850 万人六个月食用的农作物。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/floods-destroy-food-for-8-5-million-nigerians-un-estimates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 13:57:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人口增长放缓 特鲁多移民计划受质疑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/population-growth-slows-in-canada-for-first-time-since-2020</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多政府削减移民数量，加拿大人口的快速增长正在逐渐减缓。然而，该国距离大幅减少临时居民的目标还有很长的路要走——而临时居民的数量现在比以往任何时候都要大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/population-growth-slows-in-canada-for-first-time-since-2020</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 12:43:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>佐治亚州议员谴责州长拒绝接待拜登</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/georgia-s-parliament-speaker-decries-us-snub-of-prime-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[格鲁吉亚议会议长表示，美国撤回了对格鲁吉亚总理出席总统乔·拜登举办的招待会的邀请，称此举干涉了这个黑海国家的内政。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/georgia-s-parliament-speaker-decries-us-snub-of-prime-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 12:12:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工党准备改变债务规则以释放数十亿美元的借款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/labour-debt-move-opens-door-to-revival-of-green-investment-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国正在出台的一项放松严格财政规则的计划可能有助于首相基尔·斯塔默重启其雄心勃勃的气候投资计划，并回应那些批评其政府缺乏促进增长的计划的人士。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/labour-debt-move-opens-door-to-revival-of-green-investment-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 11:28:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>真主党向特拉维夫开火后以色列扩大空袭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/israel-intercepts-first-hezbollah-missile-fired-at-tel-aviv</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列在特拉维夫击落真主党发射的第一枚导弹后，加强了对黎巴嫩真主党目标自 2006 年以来最大规模的空袭。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/israel-intercepts-first-hezbollah-missile-fired-at-tel-aviv</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 07:20:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普竞选团队称已听取有关伊朗暗杀阴谋的简报</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/trump-told-of-specific-iran-assassination-plot-campaign-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普的竞选团队在一份声明中表示，拜登政府官员周二向特朗普介绍了“伊朗发出的暗杀他的真实而具体的威胁”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/trump-told-of-specific-iran-assassination-plot-campaign-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 01:24:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Ceron 称巴西财政目标将超出市场预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/brazil-fiscal-result-to-better-investor-expectations-ceron-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长罗杰里奥·塞隆周二表示，巴西 2024 年的财政业绩将好于那些对该国支撑公共财政能力持怀疑态度的投资者的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/brazil-fiscal-result-to-better-investor-expectations-ceron-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 22:10:29 GMT</pubDate>
